  }, "v8"), mdx("p", null, "Vua N\xEA-bu-c\xE1t-n\u1EBFt-xa tr\u1EA3 l\u1EDDi, \"Ta bi\u1EBFt c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i t\xECm c\xE1ch k\xE9o d\xE0i th\xEC gi\u1EDD v\xEC c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i bi\u1EBFt ta \u0111\xE3 n\xF3i l\xE0 l\xE0m. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v9"
  }, "v9"), mdx("p", null, "N\u1EBFu c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i kh\xF4ng thu\u1EADt \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c chi\xEAm bao \u0111\xF3 th\xEC c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i s\u1EBD b\u1ECB h\xECnh ph\u1EA1t. C\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\xE3 toa r\u1EADp \u0111\u1EC3 gi\u1EA3i th\xEDch l\xE1o v\xE0 b\u1ECBa \u0111\u1EB7t chuy\u1EC7n gian \xE1c, hi v\u1ECDng t\xECnh th\u1EBF s\u1EBD thay \u0111\u1ED5i. B\xE2y gi\u1EDD h\xE3y cho ta bi\u1EBFt chi\xEAm bao th\xEC ta s\u1EBD bi\u1EBFt r\u1EB1ng c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i c\xF3 th\u1EC3 gi\u1EA3i th\xEDch \xFD ngh\u0129a c\u1EE7a chi\xEAm bao \u1EA5y cho ta!\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v10"
  }, "v10"), mdx("p", null, "C\xE1c ng\u01B0\u1EDDi th\xF4ng th\xE1i th\u01B0a v\u1EDBi vua, \"Tr\xEAn tr\u1EDDi \u0111\u1EA5t n\u1EA7y kh\xF4ng ai c\xF3 th\u1EC3 l\xE0m \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c \u0111i\u1EC1u vua \u0111\xF2i c\u1EA3! Kh\xF4ng c\xF3 \u0111\u1EA1i v\u01B0\u01A1ng h\xF9ng c\u01B0\u1EDDng n\xE0o l\u1EA1i b\u1EA3o \u0111\u1ED3ng b\xF3ng, thu\u1EADt s\u0129, nh\xE0 th\xF4ng th\xE1i l\xE0m chuy\u1EC7n nh\u01B0 th\u1EBF "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v11"
  }, "v11"), mdx("p", null, "v\xEC \u0111i\u1EC1u vua \u0111\xF2i h\u1ECFi qu\xE1 kh\xF3. Ch\u1EC9 c\xF3 c\xE1c v\u1ECB th\u1EA7n kh\xF4ng s\u1ED1ng gi\u1EEFa con ng\u01B0\u1EDDi m\u1EDBi l\xE0m \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c th\xF4i.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v12"
  }, "v12"), mdx("p", null, "Khi vua nghe h\u1ECD \u0111\xE1p nh\u01B0 v\u1EADy th\xEC n\u1ED5i xung thi\xEAn. Vua li\u1EC1n ra l\u1EC7nh x\u1EED t\u1EED t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 c\xE1c nh\xE0 th\xF4ng th\xE1i trong to\xE0n n\u01B0\u1EDBc Ba-by-l\xF4n. "), mdx("h6", {
