  }, "v44"), mdx("p", null, "Trong th\u1EDDi c\xE1c vua \u1EA5y, Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF tr\xEAn tr\u1EDDi s\u1EBD l\u1EADp m\u1ED9t n\u01B0\u1EDBc kh\xF4ng bao gi\u1EDD b\u1ECB ti\xEAu di\u1EC7t hay b\u1ECB trao v\xE0o tay m\u1ED9t d\xE2n kh\xE1c. N\u01B0\u1EDBc \u1EA5y s\u1EBD t\u1ED3n t\u1EA1i m\xE3i m\xE3i sau khi \u0111\xE8 b\u1EB9p v\xE0 ti\xEAu di\u1EC7t c\xE1c n\u01B0\u1EDBc kh\xE1c. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v45"
  }, "v45"), mdx("p", null, "Th\u01B0a vua N\xEA-bu-c\xE1t-n\u1EBFt-xa, vua th\u1EA5y m\u1ED9t t\u1EA3ng \u0111\xE1 \u0111\u1EE5c ra t\u1EEB n\xFAi nh\u01B0ng kh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i do tay ng\u01B0\u1EDDi, \u0111\u1EADp n\xE1t pho t\u01B0\u1EE3ng. T\u1EA3ng \u0111\xE1 \u0111\u1EADp b\u1EC3 s\u1EAFt, \u0111\u1ED3ng, \u0111\u1EA5t s\xE9t, b\u1EA1c, v\xE0 v\xE0ng th\xE0nh t\u1EEBng m\u1EA3nh. Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF T\u1ED1i Cao \u0111\xE3 ti\u1EBFt l\u1ED9 cho vua bi\u1EBFt nh\u1EEFng bi\u1EBFn chuy\u1EC3n s\u1EBD x\u1EA3y ra. \u0110i\u1EC1m chi\xEAm bao l\xE0 th\u1EADt v\xE0 vua c\xF3 th\u1EC3 tin v\xE0o l\u1EDDi gi\u1EA3i th\xEDch n\u1EA7y.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v46"
  }, "v46"), mdx("p", null, "Vua N\xEA-bu-c\xE1t-n\u1EBFt-xa li\u1EC1n s\u1EA5p m\xECnh xu\u1ED1ng \u0111\u1EA5t tr\u01B0\u1EDBc m\u1EB7t \u0110a-ni\xEAn t\u1ECF l\xF2ng t\xF4n k\xEDnh \xF4ng. Vua ra l\u1EC7nh d\xE2ng c\u1EE7a l\u1EC5 c\xF9ng tr\u1EA7m h\u01B0\u01A1ng cho \u0110a-ni\xEAn. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v47"
  }, "v47"), mdx("p", null, "R\u1ED3i vua b\u1EA3o \u0110a-ni\xEAn, \"Th\u1EADt ta bi\u1EBFt Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF ng\u01B0\u01A1i l\u1EDBn h\u01A1n t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 c\xE1c th\u1EA7n, Ng\xE0i l\xE0 CH\xDAA c\u1EE7a c\xE1c vua. Ng\xE0i cho ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ta bi\u1EBFt nh\u1EEFng \u0111i\u1EC1u h\u1ECD kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3 bi\u1EBFt. Ta bi\u1EBFt \u0111\xFAng v\u1EADy v\xEC ng\u01B0\u01A1i c\xF3 th\u1EC3 cho ta bi\u1EBFt nh\u1EEFng \u0111i\u1EC1u huy\u1EC1n b\xED n\u1EA7y.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v48"
  }, "v48"), mdx("p", null, "Sau \u0111\xF3 vua ban th\u01B0\u1EDFng cho \u0110a-ni\xEAn \u0111\u1ED3ng th\u1EDDi giao cho \xF4ng m\u1ED9t ch\u1EE9c v\u1EE5 quan tr\u1ECDng trong n\u01B0\u1EDBc m\xECnh. Vua \u0111\u1EB7t \xF4ng cai qu\u1EA3n to\xE0n v\xF9ng Ba-by-l\xF4n v\xE0 c\u1EAFt c\u1EED \xF4ng \u0111\u1EE9ng \u0111\u1EA7u m\u1ECDi nh\xE0 th\xF4ng th\xE1i \u1EDF Ba-by-l\xF4n. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v49"
  }, "v49"), mdx("p", null, "\u0110a-ni\xEAn xin vua c\u1EED Sa-\u0111\u01A1-r\u1EAFc, M\xEA-s\xE1c, v\xE0 A-b\u1EBFt-n\xEA-g\xF4 l\xE0m quan v\xF9ng Ba-by-l\xF4n, nh\xE0 vua b\u1EB1ng l\xF2ng l\xE0m theo \u0111i\u1EC1u \u0110a-ni\xEAn y\xEAu c\u1EA7u. C\xF2n \u0110a-ni\xEAn th\xEC tr\u1EDF n\xEAn m\u1ED9t trong nh\u1EEFng c\u1EADn th\u1EA7n trong cung vua."), mdx("hr", null), mdx("p", null, "", mdx("a", {
